{
  "title": "Alert Debug",
  "tags": ["alerts", "debug"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 27,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Firing Alerts",
        "type": "table",
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 10,
          "w": 24,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\"}",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true,
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          {
            "id": "organize",
            "options": {
              "excludeByName": {
                "Time": true,
                "__name__": false
              },
              "indexByName": {},
              "renameByName": {
                "Time": "",
                "Value": "Firing",
                "__name__": "Alert Name",
                "alertname": "Alert Name",
                "instance": "Instance",
                "job": "Job",
                "severity": "Severity"
              }
            }
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": {
                "id": "byName",
                "options": "Severity"
              },
              "properties": [
                {
                  "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                  "value": {
                    "type": "color-background"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "thresholds",
                  "value": {
                    "mode": "absolute",
                    "steps": [
                      {
                        "value": null,
                        "color": "green"
                      },
                      {
                        "value": 0,
                        "color": "yellow"
                      },
                      {
                        "value": 1,
                        "color": "red"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "mappings",
                  "value": [
                    {
                      "type": "value",
                      "options": {
                        "critical": {
                          "text": "Critical",
                          "color": "red"
                        },
                        "warning": {
                          "text": "Warning",
                          "color": "yellow"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Alert Debug Instructions",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 4,
          "w": 24,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 10
        },
        "options": {
          "content": "## Alert Debug Dashboard\n\nThis dashboard shows currently firing alerts from Prometheus.\n\n**Usage:**\n- Review the table above to see all firing alerts\n- Check alert labels and severity\n- Use the runbook_url annotation to access remediation steps\n- Query individual alert expressions in Prometheus to debug\n\n**Note:** If no alerts are showing, ensure:\n1. Prometheus is scraping targets\n2. Alert rules are loaded in Prometheus\n3. Alerts have fired and are in 'firing' state"
        }
      }
    ],
    "templating": {
      "list": [
        {
          "name": "datasource",
          "type": "datasource",
          "query": "prometheus",
          "current": {
            "text": "Prometheus",
            "value": "Prometheus"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "time": {
      "from": "now-1h",
      "to": "now"
    }
}
